{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"20100-banti-to-awa-no-ousama","title":"バンティと泡（あわ）の王様（おうさま）","description":"バンティはせっけんがだいきらい。だからおふろもきらい。あるよる、バンティはゆめをみた。さあ、バンティはどうなったのでしょうか？","language":"Japanese","langCode":"ja","isRtl":false,"level":"1","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Nao S"],"illustrators":["Sorit Gupto"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"StoryWeaver Community","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/20100-banti-to-awa-no-ousama"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/720260/size3/bfaca307e321a40d4fce0bf9bade9047.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/720260/size6/bfaca307e321a40d4fce0bf9bade9047.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/2386/size6/9907217108246f4eb01c1ac7f252464b.jpg","text":"バンティは　ちょうちょと　あそぶのが　だいすき","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/2387/size6/3cfef50c731271c06bc7df15adfad696.jpg","text":"そして、とりと　あそぶのも　すき。","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/2388/size6/0b2cc2ad4ba1e7c14ab8f85d1cc92a02.jpg","text":"おりがみでつくったふねと　あそぶのがすき。","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/2389/size6/1fea81780050ff2039ff47dedfb38216.jpg","text":"すなのおしろを　つくるのも　すき。","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/2390/size6/b4b058041a0f8816ef576bb510e2a358.jpg","text":"バンティがいえにかえると、おかあさんは　「おふろにはいってきなさい！」といっても、バンティは「いやだ！」とさけんだ。","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/2391/size6/f13b791f09d8c65688476d9d6782ede2.jpg","text":"「わたしは　せっけんが　だいきらい！」と、さけんだ。","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/2392/size6/45170485855b821bd3a27a6917664b6f.jpg","text":"あるよる、バンティはゆめをみた。ばいきんが　バンティのおしろをかこんで　おそっていた。","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/2393/size6/05cc5eb1bd0a44d4e01e16ad4432d8fd.jpg","text":"バンティが　ばいきんに　おいかけられた。　バンティはひっしににげて、「たすけて！たすけて！」とさけんだ。","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/2394/size6/c3075a8fd3d40bc48a3983ac434329a7.jpg","text":"そのとき、せっけんのおうさまが　あらわれた。\n「バンティ、こわがらないで」といった。「ばいきんをやつけよう！」といって、たいりょうのあわを　ふきだした。","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/2395/size6/9e0c56e80240c4c4448a07ac8d9e80c0.jpg","text":"あわのへいたいさんたちが、ばいきんをおいはらった。","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/2396/size6/342fa90cc8f644b89f8b05984faab025.jpg","text":"それからは、バンティはせっけんがすきになり、じぶんで　はみがきと　てあらいを　するようになった。","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":11,"words":33}}